      "text": "Un zaur tawu Nahschu"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Puhſchannu irr tee Uhdeni ſakrah-"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "ti/ tee Strauti irr ſtahwejſchi itt\nka Kohpa/ tee Dſittmui irr ſa-\nſtrehjuſchi Juhras Widdu."
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Eenaidneeks ſazzija:\nEs dſihſchohs paſkat/ es panahk-\nſchu/ es dalliſchu to Laupijumu/\nimanna Dwehſele atreebſees pee\nteem. Es iſwilkſchu imannu Soh-\nbini/ un manna Rohſa tohſ iſ-\ndeldehs."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu eſſi ar tawu Wehju\npuhtis/ ta Juhra irr tohſ ap-\nkahjuſi/ tee irr nogrimmuschi itt\nka Swings warrenôs Uhdenis."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ak KUNGS! kas irr itt\nka tu ſtarp teem Deerweem? kas\nirr itt ka tu? pagohdinahts\nSwehtibâ/ zeenijains ar Teik-\ntchanahm/ Brihnumus darri-\ndams?"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu eſſi tawu labbu Roh-\nfu iſſteepis/ ta Semne irr tohſ\naprihjuſi."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu eſſi zaur tawu Scheh-\nlaſtibu ſchohs Landis waddijs/ ko\ntu eſſi atpeſtijs/ tu eſſi tohſ zaur\ntawu Spehku waddijs us tawas\nSwehtibas Mahjas-Weetu."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee Landis irr to dſirdej-\nſchi/ tee trihſehs/ Bailiba irr tohſ\naiſnehmuſi / kas Palestihná\nmahjo."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad iſtruhzinasees tee Ee-\ndoma Wirneeki / Trihſechana\nniſneins tohſ Moaba Warrenus/"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Istruhzinaschana u\nliba krittihs us teem/ zaũ\nElſona Leeliunu/ paliks te\nfu itt ka Akmins/ teekar\nKUNGS! tawi Landis\nſtaigahs/ teekams pahrst\ntee Landis/ ko tu eſſi atpe"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu iſweddiſtohſ u\ndiſi tohſ us tawas Eeman-\nnas Kalnu/ us to Weetu/\nKUNGS par tawu M\nWeetu darrijs eſſi/ us to\nWeetu/ ko tawas Roh-\nKungs! irr ſtiprinaiſchas."
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS i\nmiuſchigi muhſcham."
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo Warauis Si\nwinna Ratteim/ un ar\nJahtneekeemi irr Juhrá na-\nnn tas KUNGS irr to\nUhdeni pahr teem lizzis\nstees/ bet Israëta Behrni\nfahm Kahjahm zauc\nWiddu iſgahjuſchi."
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Mirjam ta Pra\nAärona Mahfa nehme\nBungu ſawa Rohſa/ un\nSeewas iſgahje winna\nar Bungahm un Stabule"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad atbildēja tah-\njam: Dseedajt tam KUNG\njo wiꞥſch irr fohti pa-au\njees: Sirgus un winna\nneekus irr wiꞥſch Juhrá ee"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz to likke Mol\nſraelu prohjam eet no\nJuhras/ un tee iſgahje\nTukſneſei Sur/ un tee ga"
    }
  ],
